### Member Auth API – manual test requests (VS Code REST Client / Rider .http)
@base = http://localhost:5155

### 1. Login (seeded demo member)
# @name login
POST {{base}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "jdoe",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd!"
}

### 2. Call the protected endpoint with the access token
GET {{base}}/api/v1/members/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### 3. Rotate the refresh token
POST {{base}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{login.response.body.refreshToken}}"
}

### 4. JWKS – public keys for downstream microservices
GET {{base}}/.well-known/jwks.json

### 5. OIDC-style discovery document
GET {{base}}/.well-known/openid-configuration

### 6. Health
GET {{base}}/health
